    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把主框架画出来：负载均衡器指向Creating，Creating分出三条线到Writer、Reader和IngressController。现在处理Writer内部的子状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_LoadBalancer",
        "Creating",
        "Writer",
