      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Writer里面，RedisCache连到Writing，然后Writing到Disconnecting，Disconnecting到ClosingReader，最后ClosingReader要回到Creating。Reader那边类似，但是Reading之后如果出错会进Error状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_RedisCache",
